                    <comment id="12702559" author="steve_rowe" created="Fri, 24 Apr 2009 22:21:14 +0100"  >&lt;p&gt;Implements the suggested fix: &amp;lt;code&amp;gt; is converted to &amp;lt;code&amp;gt;&amp;lt;pre&amp;gt; (instead of to &amp;amp;lt;code&amp;amp;gt; ) and &amp;lt;/code&amp;gt; is converted to &amp;lt;/pre&amp;gt;&amp;lt;/code&amp;gt; (instead of to &amp;amp;lt;/code&amp;amp;gt; )&lt;/p&gt;</comment>
